00:12:27,389 --> 00:12:30,151
I don't mean to impose, but I was just in for a procurement meeting

186
00:12:30,151 --> 00:12:32,405
with one of the joint chiefs, so I thought I'd stop by.

187
00:12:32,405 --> 00:12:35,971
- No, I'm glad you did, Lyndon. - So, how are things going?

188
00:12:35,971 --> 00:12:38,540
You know how it is. Wars are won and lost over the long haul.

189
00:12:38,540 --> 00:12:40,050
